{"tid":200754,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得LOL好多雷包","createTime":"2017-04-14T08:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T13:06:21.000Z","uid":34489,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14899789f336eaab950e1dd0b1d574ff6506c9a2","tid":200754,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"今年開季都打左三百幾場積分<br />\n依家銀牌菁英 女巫獵人 四 72分<br />\n自問有鉑金實力<br />\n(一般成日撞到鑽石玩家 對線食兵都55開 應該都冇鑽石技術都有鉑金)<br />\n<br />\n先唔講D隊友成日掛網斷線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我主上路同埋下路AD CARRY<br />\n玩上路就下路崩 玩ADC 隻上路就送<br />\n明明我都成日單殺對面 但係佢地又唔爭氣<br />\nD隊友咁垃圾 要點先凱瑞到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要正常少少既隊友都已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下大家積分要升到邊先冇呢D雷包<br />\n我諗住買分升上去就冇煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代打PM我 不過我學生哥冇乜零用 希望可以平少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />["},{"pid":"2c93a0bdb18c8973072ec5d493f441ad0313a8fd","tid":200754,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺lol好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c7e7d8e7242b1a0bef96a22320e7cd37fbeba0","tid":200754,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺唔覺lol好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺 不過玩開有感情"},{"pid":"4c7a8ac00880784d9a5638982079456f80da4ada","tid":200754,"uid":9438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"雷友呢啲野去到咩區都有"},{"pid":"15afc730df4d4b6da5e06a52d850effe73338eb1","tid":200754,"uid":2413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:46:09.00